## Responsiviteit

Mobiel-first. Volgorde: geen prefix → sm:640 → md:768 → lg:1024 → xl:1280
Desktop only: hidden lg:block
Mobiel only: lg:hidden
Grids: grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3
Sections: .ff-section (3.5rem mobiel, 5rem desktop)

---

## Shadows & radius

--shadow-soft: 0 4px 24px rgba(30,35,51,0.06)        (standaard cards)
--shadow-ring: 0 0 0 3px rgba(166,136,106,0.20)       (focus ring)
Hero CTA desktop: 0 8px 40px rgba(166,136,106,0.45)
Hero CTA mobiel:  0 4px 24px rgba(166,136,106,0.55)

--radius-lg:  1rem    (cards)
--radius-xl:  1.25rem (knoppen)
--radius-2xl: 1.5rem  (featured cards)

